 In this folder are the source file for the project npl.
main_lyric_classifier: main to read the page of the artists, extrapolate the songs, clean them, vectorize and train
			4 combinations are created: CountVec + LogReg, TfidfVec + LogReg, CountVec + RandFor, and TfidfVec + RandFor.
		
lyric_header: header file containing the functions used by main. The function extract_lyric_page is in range(10) just to avoid
		to write too many songs in the ../data/data_raw/.
 
predict_text: predict if a song snipped was written by one of the artists chosen in training. 
		Usage: from command line launch with 2 arguments
			First arg: cl, tl, cr, tr (for one of the for vec+classif combination)
			Second argument: snippet (e.g: "True blue, baby I love you")


